398
00:35:36,081 --> 00:35:37,741
Aku menemukan di mana adikmu.

399
00:35:38,718 --> 00:35:40,050
Kau menemukan Seul-ki?

400
00:35:40,784 --> 00:35:42,046
Dimana? Dimana dia?

401
00:35:42,047 --> 00:35:45,142
